The Curious Robot
=================

This is the implementation of "The Curious Robot" (TCR) project.

NOTE: it's not running yet.

# Install
TODO complete this section and add links.

TCR uses ROS and the MLR code.

To use TCR do the following:
- create a ros fuerte workspace
- add a sandbox
- create a link from ~/git/mlr/share/projects/the_curious_robot/ to ~/fuerte_workspace/sandbox/the_curious_robot
- add ~/fuerte_workspace/sandbox/the_curious_robot to the ros stack
